# LangGraph Resume Screening Workflow

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates a Resume Screening Workflow built using LangGraph.

The workflow evaluates a candidate's resume by analyzing experience and generating a hiring recommendation.

---

## Workflow

```text
START
 ↓
Extract Resume Data
 ↓
Analyze Experience
 ↓
Eligibility Check
 ↓
Generate Recommendation
 ↓
END
```

## Technologies Used

- Python
- LangGraph
- LangChain

## State Structure

```python
{
    "candidate_name": "",
    "experience_years": 0,
    "role": "",
    "decision": ""
}
```

